<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Kim Yong-sam's Remarks on Nuclear Issue Denounced </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK0403153294 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1510 GMT 4 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0403153294 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["Fool's Treacherous Color Revealed Again"--KCNA headline] </F>
  [Text] Pyongyang, March 4 (KCNA) -- The traitor Kim 
Yong-sam in a "special interview marking the 21st anniversary of 
the founding of the Korean Broadcasting System" Thursday said he 
"cannot be optimistic" about the contact of working delegates 
for the exchange of special envoys and that "optimism is a 
taboo," according to a radio report from Seoul. 
  This is a very rude outburst throwing a wet blanket over the 
North-South working contact for the exchange of special envoys 
now promoted as part of the implementation of the steps of 
simultaneous action agreed upon between the DPRK and the United 
States. It is also a sinister attempt to create artificial 
obstacles and block the exchange of special envoys. 
  Kim Yong-sam's talk about "nuclear card of the North" was 
aimed at isolating and stifling the North by branding it as a 
"nuclear culprit." 
  While taking an insincere attitude toward the exchange of 
special envoys, Kim Yong-sam claimed that unless a "meaningful 
exchange of special envoys" is realised, the United States would 
never hold the third round of talks with the North." This is an 
imprudent outcry of a fool. It is ridiculous, indeed, for the 
colonial puppet who has no interest in the settlement of the 
nuclear issue on the Korean peninsula and has no say to 
obtrusively behave as if he were a spokesman of the U.S State 
Department. 
  This meant, in other words, that the traitor Kim Yong-sam 
ordered the United States to do this or that. But the folly of 
the colonial puppet wielding the baton at his master will make a 
cat laugh. 
  The traitor also talked about the "importance of the 
cooperation system." This revealed once again his true color as 
a dyed-in-the-wool flunkeyist and heinous traitor to the nation 
who stoops to any infamy to do harm to fellow countrymen. 
  Facts show that as long as Kim Yong-sam the fool remains at 
the "presidential" post in "Chongwadae," the Korean nation 
cannot live in peace even a moment nor can the desire of the 
South Korean people for independence, democracy and national 
reunification be realised. 
  The Kim Yong-sam group engaged in treacheries will have to 
pay for the arch crime it has committed against history and the 
people. 

</TEXT>

