<F P=106> ["Anti-War, Anti-Nuke Struggle Will Gain Momentum"--KCNA </F>
headline] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, March 4 (KCNA) -- The ever-expanding 
anti-war, anti-nuke struggle of South Korean people is a just 
struggle for saving the fellow countrymen from a nuclear 
holocaust and achieving peace in the Korean peninsula, says 
MINJU CHOSON today. Commenting on the anti-war, anti-nuke 
