present in South Korea with Patriot missiles and the Kim 
Yong-sam puppet clique, dancing to its drum-beating, is making a 
frantic bid to introduce this sophisticated weapon even into the 
puppet army. 
  The planned shipment of Patriots into South Korea by the 
U.S. 
