  [Text] Hanoi VNA March 3 -- The National Assembly 
delegation led by Chairman Nong Duc Manh during its China visit 
from Feb. 21 to March 1 called at Shandong, Jiangsu, and 
Guangdong Provinces. It was accompanied by Mr Liu Suinian 
member of the National People's Congress Standing Committee, and 
other senior Chinese officials. 
  It had working sessions with delegations of provincial 
