people in general and people in Shandong, Jiangsu, Guangdong in 
particular for their persistence in building socialism, 
overcoming many difficulties to implement the open-door policy, 
and achieving important goals. 
  On behalf of the delegation, Chairman Nong Duc Manh extended 
his thanks to Chinese leaders and people for their hospitality. 
He also expressed gratitude for the Chinese people's effective 
support and assistance to the Vietnamese people in their 
struggle for national independence and national construction, as 
well as his wish for the further development of the long 
lasting, traditional friendship between the two countries. 

