  [Text] Seoul, March 7 (YONHAP) -- The government is 
speeding up its work on administrative reorganization, with an 
eye to finishing the job by month's end. 
  As the state council approved the Trade, Industry and Energy 
Ministry's reorganization plan at a meeting on Monday, the 
Government Administration Ministry will urge other ministries to 
submit their restructuring plans as soon as possible. 
