<H3> <TI>   Railroad Cut in Battambang Province 25 Feb </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK0603090594 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia in Cambodian 2330 GMT 5 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0603090594 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Cambodian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] On the night of 25 February, the people, who were 
furious with the Vietnamese communist puppets for shipping 
troops and ammunition by trains to attack and massacre them and 
plunder their property, cut off three stretches of railroad with 
a total length of 25 meters in an area between Moung and Kouk 
Trom in Battambang Province. They also cut off four other 
stretches with a total length of 200 meters in an area between 
Prey Svay and (O Krut) in the same province. 
  The people said only by doing so can the Vietnamese 
communist 
puppets be prevented from shipping troops and ammunition to 
attack and massacre them and plunder their property at will. 

</TEXT>

