Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The leader of the Fretilin independence movement in 
the Indonesian province of East Timor has challenged Jakarta to 
allow a referendum on self-determination in the former 
Portuguese colony. 
  Mr. (Niko Koni Santana) issued the challenge in a videotape 
which had been smuggled out of East Timor to the nearby 
