  [Text] Fukuoka, March 4 KYODO -- Chinese Vice Premier Zhu 
Rongji ended a 10-day visit to Japan on Friday [4 March], 
leaving for home from Fukuoka in Kyushu. 
  During his stay, Zhu met Prime Minister Morihiro Hosokawa 
and 
