  [Text] Hanoi VNA March 6 -- Prime Minister Vo Van Kiet 
received here yesterday Norwegian Ambassador to Vietnam Willy 
Johan Frederiksen who paid him a courtesy visit. 
  Prime Minister Kiet and the newly accredited ambassador 
expressed their pleasure at the development of the 
Vietnam-Norway relations of friendship and cooperation. They 
also expressed their desire to further broaden these relations 
