<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Korean </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The United States and South Korea have agreed to 
suspend the 1994 Team Spirit joint military exercise. 
  As has already been reported, the DPRK-U.S. agreement 
reached 
in New York prescribes that the United States will announce that 
South Korea agrees to suspend the 1994 Team Spirit joint 
military exercise. [sentence as heard] 
