<F P=103> SK0603090994 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 6 (KCNA) -- Papers here today 
dedicate signed articles to the 37th anniversary of the 
independence of Ghana. 
  The Ghanaian people, who achieved the independence of the 
country on March 6, 1957, have striven to consolidate national 
independence and achieve the prosperity of the country, MINJU 
