  The Ghanaian Government, pursuing the non-alignment policy 
externally, is making efforts to establish a new fair 
international order against imperialism, colonialism and racism. 
  Korea and Ghana are far away from each other geographically, 
but the two governments and peoples established and have long 
developed the relations of friendship and cooperation. 
  The Korean people, believing that the friendly and 
cooperative relations between the two countries will further 
strengthen in the future, sincerely wish the Ghanaian people 
greater success in their work to develop the economy and build a 
peaceful and stable country. 

