Federation of Trade Unions of Korea; Paek Nam-chun, director of 
the Secretariat of the Committee for the Peaceful Reunification 
of Fatherland; responsible functionaries of the sectors 
concerned; and workers of different strata in Pyongyang. 
  The meeting began with the performance of national anthem. 
  Chairman Chong Tu-hwan delivered a commemorative report at 
the meeting. [passage omitted] 

