  [Text] Pyongyang, March 7 (KCNA) -- The South Korean 
Federation of General Student Councils (Hanchongnyon) called a 
press conference at Hanyang University in Seoul on Friday and 
released a statement on the fact that a police officer belonging 
to the puppet Seoul District Police Agency had sneaked into the 
