<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["Cuban People Are Not Alone" -- KCNA headline] </F>
  [Text] Pyongyang, March 8 (KCNA) -- NODONG SINMUN today 
expresses firm solidarity with the Cuban people's just struggle 
upon the lapse of eight years since the Korean visit of Fidel 
Castro, a historical event that brought Korea-Cuba friendship to 
a higher stage. 
  Noting that the Cuban people united closely around Comrade 
Fidel Castro are steadfastly defending the sovereignty and 
dignity of the country under the banner of socialism, while 
smashing the moves of the imperialists at every turn, the paper 
